# Verification Steps

## Code Quality Checks
- Ensure all code passes linting and formatting checks.
- Verify that all components and functions have appropriate test coverage.

## Functional Testing
- Test all user flows manually to ensure they work as expected.
- Use automated tests to verify critical paths.

## Integration Testing
- Ensure all API integrations are functioning correctly.
- Test error handling and edge cases thoroughly.

## Deployment
- Verify that the app builds successfully for both iOS and Android.
- Ensure that the app passes all deployment checks and is ready for release.
